data.description: Seller will entertain all offers!! Beautiful home located in Rolling Hills Estates. Stainless steel microwave and stove/oven. Vaulted ceiling in the living room for an open feel. Covered patio in the HUGE fenced in backyard. Washer, dryer and 2nd refrigerator included. Roof replaced in 2021, water heater 2020 and exterior of house painted in 2020. Home is 3/2 with primary downstairs, 2 bedrooms and a versatile bonus room upstairs. This corner lot is one of the biggest lots in the neighborhood. Come and see this beautiful home and all the amazing work the sellers have put in it.
